(In reply to Toghrul from comment #3)

With Electron 5 and later, it is required to explicitly enable webviewTag for using webview tags.

The line in the sample JavaScript code:

win = new BrowserWindow({width: 800, height: 600})

should look like this:

win = new BrowserWindow({
  width: 800,
  height: 600,
  webPreferences: {
    webviewTag: true
  }
})

cf. https://www.electronjs.org/docs/latest/breaking-changes#planned-breaking-api-changes-50
